description: Russia puts up a wall of denial as it stands accused over the Malaysian jet shot down in 2014.
title: Flight MH17 disaster: Russia scorns 'political' murder trial
title_page: Flight MH17 disaster: Russia scorns 'political' murder trial - BBC News
maintext: "We're not talking about what organisation they belonged to," she replies. "How are those two guys connected to what happened to the Skripals? Probably they were near this place. Probably they touched something. Probably they - I don't know - gave him some medicine. What happened? Can you tell me?"
